te House Press Secretary. He was also the recipient of a letter from Emperor Haile Selassie regarding the annexation of Eritrea and Italian Somaliland. Furthermore, Roosevelt first used the term \"State of the Union\" in 1934, setting a precedent for future presidential addresses. His predecessor was Harry S. Truman, and his policies, particularly the New Deal, have left a lasting impact on American history."}
